              <h3>
               Notes
              </h3>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              The answer will always be between -floor((
              <b>
               n
              </b>
              -1)/2) and floor(
              <b>
               n
              </b>
              /2), inclusive.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              Beware of overflow.
             </td>
            </tr>
